import React from 'react';
import { Box, Stack, Typography, Link, IconButton } from '@mui/material';
import FacebookIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Facebook';
import TwitterIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Twitter';
import InstagramIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Instagram';
import EmailIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Email';

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <Box mt="80px" bgcolor="#ffa9a9" py="40px">
      <Stack gap="40px" sx={{ alignItems: 'center' }} flexWrap="wrap" px="40px">
        <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontSize: { lg: '28px', xs: '20px' } }}>
          About Us
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontSize: { lg: '28px', xs: '20px' } }}>
          Contact Us
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontSize: { lg: '28px', xs: '20px' } }}>
          Support
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontSize: { lg: '28px', xs: '20px' } }}>
          Social Media
        </Typography>
      </Stack>
      <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontSize: { lg: '28px', xs: '20px' } }} mt="20px" textAlign="center" pt='10px'>
        Copyright © BStrong
      </Typography>
      <Stack gap="10px" sx={{ justifyContent: 'center' }} mt="20px">
        <Link href="https://www.facebook.com/yourpage">
          <IconButton>
            <FacebookIcon />
          </IconButton>
        </Link>
        <Link href="https://twitter.com/yourhandle">
          <IconButton>
            <TwitterIcon />
          </IconButton>
        </Link>
        <Link href="https://www.instagram.com/yourprofile">
          <IconButton>
            <InstagramIcon />
          </IconButton>
        </Link>
        <Link href="mailto:your@email.com">
          <IconButton>
            <EmailIcon />
          </IconButton>
        </Link>
      </Stack>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default Footer;
